# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:13
translate chinese suzypersonal1_0305dee2:

    # pc "Do you ever talk to your real dad?"
    pc "你和亲生父亲有联系吗？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:15
translate chinese suzypersonal1_3f50f500:

    # ss "Not really. He calls on my birthday sometimes when he remembers."
    ss "没什么联系。他偶尔会在我生日那天打个电话，如果他记得的话。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:16
translate chinese suzypersonal1_b137dcc6:

    # ss "He and mom split up when I was four. And he's gone a little crazy since then - conspiracy nut who is constantly posting ridiculous memes online."
    ss "我四岁那年，他和妈妈分开了。从那以后，他就有点疯了——成了个阴谋论狂热分子，整天在网上发些荒谬的梗图。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:17
translate chinese suzypersonal1_1827b67e:

    # ss "I don't really like him all that much, honestly."
    ss "说实话，我其实不太喜欢他。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:18
translate chinese suzypersonal1_bed6ad0f:

    # ss "And I'm glad he lives all the way across the country. I haven't seen him in like five years now."
    ss "而且我很高兴他住在遥远的另一头。我大概有五年没见过他了。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:19
translate chinese suzypersonal1_97748ea9:

    # ss "As far as I'm concerned, your dad is my dad."
    ss "对我来说，你爸就是我爸。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:20
translate chinese suzypersonal1_2600d93d:

    # ss "He's treated me more like a daughter than my real dad ever did."
    ss "他待我比我亲生父亲还要像亲生父亲一样。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:22
translate chinese suzypersonal1_2ff4738e:

    # ss "I wish he were here."
    ss "真希望他能在这里。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:23
translate chinese suzypersonal1_107f9102:

    # pc "We'll find him."
    pc "我们会找到他的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzypersonal1.rpy:24
translate chinese suzypersonal1_3dff063d:

    # ss "I hope so."
    ss "我也希望如此。"

